item.title: Longines Global Champions Tour 2023
item.dc:creator: Antonie Cruz
item.description: We are proud to participate in the largest global event “Longines Global Champions Tour 2023” 2023 edition in Doha, Qatar. Enjoy watching the Global champions & their horses directly from the balcony of Café Noir and enjoy the best taste of coffee specially imported from the best international roasters in Italy
item.content:encoded:
We are proud to participate in the largest global event “Longines Global Champions Tour 2023” 2023 edition in Doha, Qatar.

Enjoy watching the Global champions & their horses directly from the balcony of Café Noir and enjoy the best taste of coffee specially imported from the best international roasters in Italy
